  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\"><img alt=\"House Umber.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Umber.svg/50px-House_Umber.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Umber.svg/75px-House_Umber.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/House_Umber.svg/100px-House_Umber.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Osric Umber</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\"><img alt=\"House Umber.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Umber.svg/50px-House_Umber.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Umber.svg/75px-House_Umber.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/House_Umber.svg/100px-House_Umber.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Last_Hearth\" title=\"Lord of the Last Hearth\">Lord of the Last Hearth</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Title_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Title-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\">House Umber</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_215_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">215&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_165_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">165</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_226_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">226&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arrana_Stark\" title=\"Arrana Stark\">Arrana Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nChild(ren)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (appendix)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Osric Umber</b> was the Lord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Last_Hearth\" title=\"Last Hearth\">Last Hearth</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\">House Umber</a> during the latter half of the second century after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Title_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Title-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Osric_Umber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Osric was married to <a href=\"/index.php/Arrana_Stark\" title=\"Arrana Stark\">Arrana Stark</a>, the older daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Edric_Stark\" title=\"Edric Stark\">Edric Stark</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Serena_Stark\" title=\"Serena Stark\">Serena Stark</a>. Together, the couple had issue.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Osric_Umber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>His relation to <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Umber_(husband_of_Serena)\" title=\"Jon Umber (husband of Serena)\">Jon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Harmond_Umber\" title=\"Harmond Umber\">Harmond Umber</a>, the Lords of the Last Hearth before and after him respectively, are unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Osric_Umber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Title-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Title_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Title_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">asoiaf.westeros.org: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/152844-the-wiki-timeline-project-v2/&amp;page=5&amp;tab=comments#comment-8495418\">The Wiki-Timeline Project v2 &#8211; Comment by Ran (March 16, 2020)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Calculation-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued2)#Osric_Umber\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued2)\">Osric Umber</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Appendix: Stark Lineage.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Last known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Umber_(husband_of_Serena)\" title=\"Jon Umber (husband of Serena)\">Jon Umber</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Last_Hearth\" title=\"Lord of the Last Hearth\">Lord of the Last Hearth</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Harmond_Umber\" title=\"Harmond Umber\">Harmond Umber</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403145212\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.092 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.325 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 715/